steps.name: The user navigates to the Shopping Website
The user is navigated to the login page
The user enters the username "standard_user" and password "secret_sauce"
The user clicks the login button
The user is presented with shopping screen with a list of items to shop
The user adds item "0" to the shopping cart
The user adds item "1" to the shopping cart
The cart icon displays "2" items on the list
The user clicks the cart icon
The user is navigated to the cart summary page
The user is presented with a correct list of cart items
The user is presented with the checkout info page
The user enters the customer name "Sibusiso" the customer surname "Radebe" and the zipcode "4491"
The customer continue from the checkout information page
The user is navigated to the checkout overview page
The pre tax total item price is calculated correctly
The user clicks the finish button
